---
title: Chorizo-Apple Stuffing Bowls with Sage Gravy
description: Everyone's favourite part of holiday dinners is the stuffing, so why not make it the star? Our chorizo, apple and potato stuffing bowl will have you longing to cozy up in front of a fireplace!
